2. cs.LG (Machine Learning) is also likely as the paper uses deep reinforcement learning for optimization. 
3. cs.AI (Artificial Intelligence) is another possible category as the paper deals with intelligent systems that can automatically age-progress facial images. 
4. cs.MM (Multimedia) is a possible category as the paper deals with video processing and facial image synthesis. 
5. cs.HC (Human-Computer Interaction) is also a possible category as the paper deals with the preservation of visual identity and cross-age face verification, which are relevant to human perception and interaction with technology.
